                <h4>Complementary Courses (10 credits)</h4>

    
              <p>10 credits selected as specified below:</p>
    
      
      
                <h4>Physical Activity</h4>

    
              <p>4 credits of Physical Activity courses (EDKP) offered by the Department of Kinesiology and Physical Education.</p>
    
      
      
                <h4>Multicultural Education</h4>

    
              <p>3 credits from:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/edec-233" class="program-course-title">
